# REST Assured + TestNG API Automation Framework

This project is  **API test automation framework** built using **REST Assured**, **TestNG**, and **Java**. 

## Tech Stack

- [REST Assured](https://rest-assured.io/) – API testing library for Java
- [TestNG](https://testng.org/) – Testing framework for running and managing tests
- [JSON] – For JSON parsing 
- [Log4j2] - For log files
- [Extent Reports ] – For test reporting
- [Maven] – Project build and dependency management


## Project Structure
project-root/

├── src      
│    └── main/
│    │    └── java/
│    │          └── com/
│	 │	             └── api/
│    │                    ├── config/   
│    │                    │      └── GlobalConfiguration.java      # Load configuration
│	 │	   	  	          │
│    │                    └── model/                            
│    │                           ├── BaseRequest.java              # Base Request class that encapsulate the common behaviours
│	 │			                 ├── GetRequest.java               # Get Request that extends the Base Request
│	 │			                 └── PostRequest.java
│    │
│    └── test/                      
│         ├── java                                   
│         │    └──interview                    
│         │            ├── BaseTest.java 			    # Base Test class that encapsulate the common behaviours
│         │            ├── CountriesAPITest		        # Test scenarios
│         │            └── TestNGListener				# TestNGListener that log test lifecycle and integrates ExtentReports   
│         └── resources
│               ├──schema                                  
│               │    └──restcountries_schema.json       # schema
│			    ├── config.properties                   # configuration file for Base URL 
│			    └── log4j2.xml                          # log4j2 configuration file
│
│
│
├── logs
│     └── test.log                     # log file
│
├── target
│     └── report.html                  # Report
├── Dockerfile                     
├── testng.xml                         # TestNG suite definition
│
├── pom.xml                            # Maven project descriptor
└── README

Prerequisites

  Java 11
  Maven
  IDE (e.g. IntelliJ, Eclipse)
  
Install dependencies
  mvn clean install
  
Run all tests
  mvn test
  
  
## Docker (win10)
In project-root：
docker build -t securitease_api-testng:latest .
docker run --rm -v "%cd%\reports:/app/target" securitease_api-testng:latest
map /app/target to reports
	